	<module type="driver" id="sam.drivers.pdc" caption="PDC - Peripheral DMA Controller Example">
		<info type="description" value="summary">
			The Peripheral DMA Controller transfers data between on-chip serial peripherals
			and the on- and/or off-chip memories. The link between the PDC and a serial
			peripheral is operated by the AHB to ABP bridge.
		</info>
